🗝️ 📚
🧩 fib(n) 👉
   ❓ n ⚖️ 0 👉
      ✅ 0
   🔚
   ❓ n ⚖️ 1 👉
      ✅ 1
   🔚
   ❗ 👉
      n1 ⬅️ 差(n, 1)
      n2 ⬅️ 差(n, 2)
      fib1 ⬅️ fib(n1)
      fib2 ⬅️ fib(n2)
      ✅ 和(fib1, fib2)
   🔚
🔚
>>> fib(10) 
55
>>> fib(1) 
1
>>> fib(8) 
21
>>> fib(10) 
55
>>> fib(1) 
1
>>> fib(8) 
21
>>> fib(11) 
89
>>> fib(12) 
144